               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18350202-name-703" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18350202-name-703" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18350202-name-703" type="surname" value="COLLIER"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18350202-name-703" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN COLLIER</persName>
                  </hi>. I keep a coal and potato warehouse in Bell-street, Lisson-grove. On the 28th of January, I was sitting in the parlour—I heard, as I thought, some one in the shop—I looked, but I saw no one—in half a minute, I heard the scales rattle—I ran out, the scales were gone—I went out, and took the prisoner under a gateway with them.</p>
